           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY uniquepid ORDER BY hospitaladmittime) as visit_rank,
           patientunitstayid
    FROM patient
),
target_patient_age AS (
    SELECT age
    FROM patient_first_visit
    WHERE uniquepid = '027-14712' AND visit_rank = 1
),
same_age_patients AS (
    SELECT pf.patientunitstayid
    FROM patient_first_visit pf
    CROSS JOIN target_patient_age tpa
    WHERE pf.age = tpa.age AND pf.visit_rank = 1
),
phosphate_values AS (
    SELECT l.labresult
    FROM lab l
    JOIN same_age_patients sap ON l.patientunitstayid = sap.patientunitstayid
    WHERE l.labname = 'phosphate'
)
SELECT 
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM phosphate_values WHERE labresult < 3.1) * 100.0 / 
    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM phosphate_values) as percentile
FROM (SELECT 1) dummy;

    SELECT patienthealthsystemstayid, patientunitstayid
    FROM patient 
    WHERE uniquepid = '017-24595'
    ORDER BY hospitaladmittime DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
all_tests AS (
    SELECT 
        l.labname as testname,
        l.labresulttime as testtime,
        'lab' as testtype
    FROM lab l
    INNER JOIN last_visit lv ON l.patientunitstayid = lv.patientunitstayid
    
    UNION ALL
    
    SELECT 
        CONCAT('culture - ', m.culturesite, ' - ', m.organism) as testname,
        m.culturetakentime as testtime,
        'microlab' as testtype
    FROM microlab m
    INNER JOIN last_visit lv ON m.patientunitstayid = lv.patientunitstayid
)
SELECT testname, testtime, testtype
FROM all_tests
ORDER BY testtime DESC
LIMIT 1;

predict:
WITH pain_diagnosed_patients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT p.patientunitstayid, p.unitadmittime, p.hospitaldischargestatus, p.hospitaldischargetime, d.diagnosistime
    FROM patient p
    JOIN diagnosis d ON p.patientunitstayid = d.patientunitstayid
    WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%pain%'
),
albuterol_after_pain AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT pdp.patientunitstayid, pdp.unitadmittime, pdp.hospitaldischargestatus, pdp.hospitaldischargetime
    FROM pain_diagnosed_patients pdp
    JOIN medication m ON pdp.patientunitstayid = m.patientunitstayid
    WHERE m.drugname = 'albuterol 2.5 mg/0.5ml ud inh soln'
    AND m.drugstarttime > pdp.diagnosistime
),

    SELECT 
        patientunitstayid,
        CASE 
            WHEN hospitaldischargestatus = 'alive' THEN 1
            WHEN hospitaldischargestatus = 'expired' AND 
                 (hospitaldischargetime IS NULL OR 
                  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM AGE(hospitaldischargetime, unitadmittime)) >= 5) THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS survived_5_years
    FROM albuterol_after_pain
)
SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS total_patients,
    SUM(survived_5_years) AS survived_patients,
    ROUND(100.0 * SUM(survived_5_years) / COUNT(*), 2) AS survival_rate_percent
FROM survival_analysis;

input: among patients who were prescribed clonazepam 0.5 mg po tabs what were the five most frequently ordered drugs at t
predict:
WITH clonazepam_patients AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT m1.patientunitstayid,
           m1.drugstarttime as clonazepam_start,
           m1.drugstoptime as clonazepam_stop
    FROM medication m1
    WHERE LOWER(m1.drugname) LIKE '%clonazepam%'
      AND LOWER(m1.dosage) LIKE '%0.5 mg%'
      AND LOWER(m1.routeadmin) LIKE '%po%'
      AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM m1.drugstarttime) = 2102
),
concurrent_medications AS (
    SELECT m2.drugname,
           COUNT(*) as frequency
    FROM clonazepam_patients cp
    JOIN medication m2 ON cp.patientunitstayid = m2.patientunitstayid
    WHERE NOT (LOWER(m2.drugname) LIKE '%clonazepam%' 
               AND LOWER(m2.dosage) LIKE '%0.5 mg%'
               AND LOWER(m2.routeadmin) LIKE '%po%')
      AND ((m2.drugstarttime <= cp.clonazepam_stop OR cp.clonazepam_stop IS NULL)
           AND (m2.drugstoptime >= cp.clonazepam_start OR m2.drugstoptime IS NULL))
    GROUP BY m2.drugname
)
SELECT drugname, frequency
FROM concurrent_medications
ORDER BY frequency DESC
LIMIT 5;

input: in the last year, what are the top five most frequent lab tests given to patients in the same month after being diagnose
predict:
SELECT 
    l.labname,
    COUNT(*) as frequency
FROM diagnosis d
JOIN patient p ON d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
JOIN lab l ON d.patientunitstayid = l.patientunitstayid
WHERE d.diagnosisname LIKE '%esophageal%ca%'
    AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosistime) = 2105
    AND l.labresulttime > d.diagnosistime
    AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM l.labresulttime) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM d.diagnosistime)
    AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM l.labresulttime) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM d.diagnosistime)
GROUP BY l.labname
ORDER BY frequency DESC
LIMIT 5;
real: select t3.labname from ( select t2.labname, dense_rank() over ( order by count(*) desc ) as c1 from ( select patient.uniquepid, diagnosis.diagnosistime from diagnosis join patient on diagnosis.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where diagnosis.diagnosisname = 'esophageal ca' and datetime(diagnosis.diagnosistime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t1 join ( select patient.uniquepid, lab.labname, lab.labresulttime from lab join patient on lab.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid where datetime(lab.labresulttime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year','-1 year') ) as t2 on t1.uniquepid = t2.uniquepid where t1.diagnosistime < t2.labresulttime and datetime(t1.diagnosistime,'start of month') = datetime(t2.labresulttime,'start of month') group by t2.labname ) as t3 where t3.c1 <= 5;
pred:
select 
    l.labname,
    count(*) as frequency
from diagnosis d
join patient p on d.patientunitstayid = p.patientunitstayid
join lab l on d.patientunitstayid = l.patientunitstayid
where d.diagnosisname like '%esophageal%ca%'
    and extract(year from d.diagnosistime) = 2105
    and l.labresulttime > d.diagnosistime
    and extract(year from l.labresulttime) = extract(year from d.diagnosistime)
    and extract(month from l.labresulttime) = extract(month from d.diagnosistime)
group by l.labname
order by frequency desc
limit 5;
